From Larry Caldwell Subject Re SUNDAY THE DAY OF OUR LORD Paul Harvey writes Darius Lecointe writes Exactly Sunday worship is in honor or the SUN , not the SON of God Same thing, isn't it It's pronounced the same What other heavenly beings are resurrected The moon That would by lunacy, at least to a sunday worshiper I have heard that the sabbath was originally determined by the phases of the moon, and had elements of moon worship Early stuff, Egyptian in nature Larry Caldwell CompuServe , Oregon Health Sciences University